<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<odoo>
  <template id="aboutus" name="About AAOI">
    <t t-call="portal.portal_layout">
      <t t-set="breadcrumbs_searchbar" t-value="True"/>
      <!--  Navbar breadcrumb  -->
      <t t-if="breadcrumbs_searchbar">
        <t t-call="portal.portal_breadcrumbs"/>
      </t>
      <div id="wrap_about" class="oe_structure oe_empty mt16 aaoi_aboutus_container">
        <section id="aaoi_snippet_cover">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md img-container">
                <img src="/aaoi_website/static/src/img/ppa.png"/>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-7 text-white">
                <h1 class="aaoi_customized_training_title">ArkeUp Academy,
                  <br/>
                  excellence and innovation
                </h1>
                <p class="aaoi_customized_training_text font-weight-light">
                  Digital technology is currently booming in Madagascar in all sectors of activity. The State is, among
                  other things, very committed to the digital transformation process.
                </p>
                <p class="aaoi_customized_training_text font-weight-light">
                  I was convinced that eTech- ArkeUp group, as the number 1 digital company in the area, had to
                  participate in the collective effort to achieve this goal. It is with this vision that we created
                  ArkeUp Academy Indian Ocean. Our mission is to train students, professionals, and collaborators of our
                  colleagues, as well as
                  to accompany public and private bodies in new, innovative fields that are recognized in international
                  countries.
                </p>
                <div class="signature font-weight-light">
                  <strong class="text-white font-weight-bold">Pierre Paul ARDILE</strong>
                  <br/>
                  CEO - Arkeup Group
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        <section id="aaoi_tree_column">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="mx-auto mr-md-auto w-fixed">
                  <h2 class="aaoi_banner_snippets_other_tittle mb-3">
                    Our vision
                  </h2>
                  <p class="aaoi_banner_snippets_other_text_text mb-0">
                    At ArkeUp Academy, we know and believe that becoming an expert in a field that we are passionate
                    about is the best passionate about is the best satisfaction one can have.
                  </p>
                </div>

              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="mx-auto w-fixed">
                  <h2 class="aaoi_banner_snippets_other_tittle mb-3">
                    Our mission
                  </h2>
                  <p class="aaoi_banner_snippets_other_text_text mb-0">
                    Accompany any individual or company wishing to achieve excellence in their chosen field.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="mx-auto ml-md-auto w-fixed">
                  <h2 class="aaoi_banner_snippets_other_tittle mb-3">
                    Our values
                  </h2>
                  <p class="aaoi_banner_snippets_other_text_text mb-0">
                    Excellence
                    <br/>
                    Innovation
                    <br/>
                    Commitment
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        <section id="aaoi_methodology">
          <div class="container">
            <img class="cofee-img" src="/aaoi_website/static/src/img/bulb-dynamic-color.svg"/>
            <h2 class="aaoi_learn_more_snippets_title mb16">
              Methodology
            </h2>
            <p class="font-weight-light mb32">
              ArkeUp Academy Indian Ocean training courses are high level courses, initiated by experienced trainers,
              both pedagogically and practically.
            </p>
            <div class="aaoi-row">
              <div class="aaoi-col">
                <h3 class="aaoi_banner_snippets_other_tittle font-weight-light">
                  <strong
                      class="aaoi_learn_more_snippets_title number">1.
                  </strong>
                  Pre-training
                </h3>
                <p class="aaoi_banner_snippets_other_text_text font-weight-bold">
                  The profile of each candidate is studied before registration in order to offer them a curriculum that
                  is more adapted to their level.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="aaoi-col">
                <h3 class="aaoi_banner_snippets_other_tittle font-weight-light">
                  <strong
                      class="aaoi_learn_more_snippets_title number">2.
                  </strong>
                  Training
                </h3>
                <p class="aaoi_banner_snippets_other_text_text font-weight-bold">
                  The quality of the training is our guideline. Each participant is accompanied according to his or her
                  learning pace.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="aaoi-col">
                <h3 class="aaoi_banner_snippets_other_tittle font-weight-light">
                  <strong
                      class="aaoi_learn_more_snippets_title number">3.
                  </strong>
                  Evaluation
                </h3>
                <p class="aaoi_banner_snippets_other_text_text font-weight-bold">
                  At the end of each course, an evaluation will be made to materialize the acquired knowledge. The grade
                  is attributed according to precise scales.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="aaoi-col">
                <h3 class="aaoi_banner_snippets_other_tittle font-weight-light">
                  <strong
                      class="aaoi_learn_more_snippets_title number">4.
                  </strong>
                  Follow-up
                </h3>
                <p class="aaoi_banner_snippets_other_text_text font-weight-bold">
                  We provide your employees with a PDF version of the course material so that they can follow the
                  courses virtually.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
